{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build Section 2 directly below the hero section.
    
    SECTION GOAL
    
    This section must immediately show visitors and Google Ads what services Titan Express provides.
    
    The design should increase landing page relevance, improve Google Ads Quality Score, strengthen SEO signals, and help customers quickly identify the service they need.
    
    SECTION TITLE
    
    What Can We Move For You?
    
    SUBHEADING
    
    From single-item furniture delivery to apartment moves and Marketplace pickups, Titan Express provides fast, affordable moving and delivery services throughout Sydney.
    
    LAYOUT
    
    Create a premium responsive service grid.
    
    Desktop:
    3 columns
    
    Tablet:
    2 columns
    
    Mobile:
    1 column
    
    Use modern service cards with hover animations, subtle shadows, glassmorphism effects, SVG icons and smooth transitions.
    
    SERVICE CARDS
    
    Furniture Delivery Sydney
    
    Description:
    Sofas, dining tables, beds, wardrobes, entertainment units and household furniture delivered across Sydney.
    
    Icon:
    Modern sofa SVG
    
    ---
    
    Marketplace Pickup & Delivery
    
    Description:
    Facebook Marketplace, Gumtree and private seller pickups delivered directly to your home.
    
    Icon:
    Location pin + package SVG
    
    ---
    
    Man and Van Sydney
    
    Description:
    Affordable moving help with an oversized long-wheelbase van and professional mover.
    
    Icon:
    Modern van SVG
    
    ---
    
    Small Apartment Moves
    
    Description:
    Studio apartments, one-bedroom units and small household relocations.
    
    Icon:
    Apartment building SVG
    
    ---
    
    Store Collection Delivery
    
    Description:
    Furniture pickups from IKEA, Fantastic Furniture, Freedom, Amart and retail stores.
    
    Icon:
    Storefront SVG
    
    ---
    
    Single Item Delivery
    
    Description:
    Fridges, washing machines, mattresses, lounges and bulky household items.
    
    Icon:
    Package delivery SVG
    
    ---
    
    Granny Flat Moves
    
    Description:
    Affordable relocation assistance for granny flats and smaller homes.
    
    Icon:
    House SVG
    
    ---
    
    Same Day Delivery
    
    Description:
    Urgent furniture pickups and deliveries available across Sydney.
    
    Icon:
    Fast delivery route SVG
    
    INTERACTIVE REQUIREMENTS
    
    Each service card should include:
    
    • Hover lift animation
    • Border glow effect
    • Animated icon movement
    • Smooth transitions
    • Mobile touch feedback
    • Expandable "Learn More" interaction
    • Modern card shadows
    • Floating background elements
    
    VISUAL STYLE
    
    Premium service-business appearance.
    
    Colours:
    White
    Black
    Gold
    Yellow
    Small blue accents
    
    Use modern SVG illustrations.
    
    Avoid stock-looking icons.
    
    BACKGROUND
    
    Create a subtle SVG pattern background.
    
    Use:
    
    • Route lines
    • Delivery paths
    • Location markers
    • Abstract moving elements
    
    Keep the design clean and professional.
    
    SEO REQUIREMENTS
    
    Naturally include:
    
    Removalist Sydney
    
    Furniture Delivery Sydney
    
    Man and Van Sydney
    
    Marketplace Pickup Delivery Sydney
    
    Single Item Delivery Sydney
    
    Small Apartment Moves Sydney
    
    Store Collection Delivery Sydney
    
    Same Day Delivery Sydney
    
    Do not keyword stuff.
    
    GOOGLE ADS RELEVANCE
    
    This section should clearly communicate:
    
    Who we help
    
    What we move
    
    Where we operate
    
    Why customers choose Titan Express
    
    Trust indicators:
    
    ✓ Professional Handling
    
    ✓ Oversized Van
    
    ✓ Furniture Protection
    
    ✓ Sydney Wide Service
    
    ✓ Same Day Availability
    
    OUTPUT
    
    Generate complete Shopify-compatible Liquid, HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
    
    Use class names beginning with:
    
    titan-services-
    
    Make the section highly responsive, interactive, conversion-focused and visually premium while maintaining fast loading performance.
      yelloww white black theme
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .titan-services-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .titan-services-background-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    opacity: {{ block.settings.background_pattern_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .titan-services-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .titan-services-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .titan-services-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_spacing }}px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .titan-services-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .titan-services-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.grid_spacing }}px;
  }

  .titan-services-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    border: {{ block.settings.card_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    backdrop-filter: blur({{ block.settings.glassmorphism_blur }}px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .titan-services-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{ block.settings.card_gradient_start }} 0%, {{ block.settings.card_gradient_end }} 100%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .titan-services-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover::before {
    opacity: {{ block.settings.card_gradient_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};
  }

  .titan-services-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-{{ block.settings.hover_lift }}px);
    box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.hover_shadow_y }}px {{ block.settings.hover_shadow_blur }}px rgba(0, 0, 0, {{ block.settings.hover_shadow_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }});
    border-color: {{ block.settings.card_hover_border_color }};
  }

  .titan-services-card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .titan-services-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.icon_spacing }}px;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .titan-services-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .titan-services-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: translateY(-{{ block.settings.icon_hover_move }}px) scale(1.05);
  }

  .titan-services-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .titan-services-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.card_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.card_title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.card_title_spacing }}px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .titan-services-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .titan-services-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.card_title_hover_color }};
  }

  .titan-services-card-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.card_description_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.card_description_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .titan-services-learn-more-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.learn_more_spacing }}px;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease, opacity 0.4s ease;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .titan-services-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.expanded .titan-services-learn-more-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 200px;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .titan-services-learn-more-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.learn_more_text_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.learn_more_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .titan-services-trust-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.trust_section_spacing }}px;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.trust_section_padding }}px;
    border-top: 1px solid {{ block.settings.trust_border_color }};
  }

  .titan-services-trust-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .titan-services-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.trust_text_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.trust_text_color }};
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .titan-services-trust-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: {{ block.settings.trust_icon_color }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .titan-services-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .titan-services-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.title_size }}px * 0.8);
    }

    .titan-services-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px * 0.9);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .titan-services-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.7 }}px 16px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .titan-services-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap | times: 0.75 }}px;
    }

    .titan-services-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.title_size }}px * 0.65);
    }

    .titan-services-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .titan-services-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .titan-services-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.85 }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.85 }}px;
    }

    .titan-services-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.card_title_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    .titan-services-trust-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .titan-services-trust-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.trust_text_size }}px * 0.9);
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

